uk.ac.ebi.kraken.interfaces.uniprot

Interface Keyword

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasEvidences, Serializable, Value

    public interface Keyword
extends Value, HasEvidences
    A single Keyword in the Keyword annotation of the UniProtEntry.

    These values can be found in the KW line of the flat file on the marked position. 
       ...
 DR   ProDom; PD000375; Cyt_CIAB; 1.
 DR   PROSITE; PS51007; CYTC; 1.
 KW   Acetylation; Apoptosis; Direct protein sequencing; Electron transport;
 KW   Heme; Mitochondrion; Polymorphism; Respiratory chain.
 FT   INIT_MET      0      0
 FT   MOD_RES       1      1       N-acetylglycine.
 ...
    In the internal section of TrEMBL entries, Keywords can be assigned with Evidence Tags, which are resolved in the **EV line of the entry 
       ...
 DR   SMART; SM00289; WR1; 3.
 DR   PROSITE; PS50279; BPTI_KUNITZ_2; 7.
 KW   Complete proteome{EI5}; Hypothetical protein{EP2}.
 **
 **   #################    INTERNAL SECTION    ##################
 **EV EI5; ProtImp; -; -; 31-MAY-2005.
 **EV EP2; TrEMBL; -; CAA94800.1; 20-AUG-2005.
 ...
    In XML: 
     ...
 <dbReference type="PROSITE" id="PS51007" key="69">
   <property type="entry name" value="CYTC"/>
   <property type="match status" value="1"/>
 </dbReference>
 <keyword id="KW-0007">Acetylation</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0053">Apoptosis</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0903">Direct protein sequencing</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0249">Electron transport</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0349">Heme</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0496">Mitochondrion</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0621">Polymorphism</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0679">Respiratory chain</keyword>
 <feature type="initiator methionine">
   <location>
     <position position="0"/>
   </location>
 </feature>
 ...
    Evidence Tags are resolved with the evidence attribute of the keyword tag and the key attribute of the evidence tag: 
     ...
 <keyword id="KW-0181" evidence="EI3">Complete proteome</keyword>
 <keyword id="KW-0384" evidence="EP4">Hypothetical protein</keyword>
 <evidence category="import" type="ProtImp" date="2005-05-31" key="EI3"/>
 <evidence category="program" type="TrEMBL" attribute="CAA94800.1" date="2005-08-20" key="EP4"/>
 ...
